      "text": "アンケート、そろそろ出さなきゃいけないんだけどね",
      "startTime": 70.6679139896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。んー……\nなら、ほしいものとかない？",
      "startTime": 79.5666662335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "『こういうものがほしいから、買いに行きたいです』\nって書くのもありだと思う",
      "startTime": 85.6225924457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "ショッピング企画か～、たまに見るよね\nスタッフさんにじゃんけんで勝ったらプレゼント、とか",
      "startTime": 91.2999995668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_51_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "うん、王道で面白いと思う\n何かほしいものない？　興味があるものでもいいし",
      "startTime": 97.7999995668,
      "sfxList": []
